add Prisma:
yarn add prisma --save-dev

add Prisma Client:
yarn add @prisma/client

Iniate Prisma in project:
npx prisma init

Generate Prisma:
npx prisma generate

Prisma Push to DB:
npx prisma db push

Add bcrypt:
yarn add bcrypt

Add next-auth:
yarn add next-auth

Add Prisma Adaptor:
yarn add @next-auth/prisma-adaptor